@node system

                     System Requirements

		Computer : Amiga 500-4000
		Kickstart: 3.0+

		     HD is recommended

@endnode

@node Intro

                         Introduction

The Cataloger is shareware ! 
Have you ever had the problem to find a file on 10 CDs ?
If you want to find a file in such a package you have to put the first CD
in your drive and look if the file is present, put the second CD in drive...

And now it is possible with this tool to make a index-file of every CD 
(or HD). After that you can select in which Catalogs you want to look.
Now the CATALOGER gives you the full path of the file. The only thing to do is
put the CD in drive the CATALOGER tells you and use the searched and found file :).

This Version is over and over with 'remind-requesters',

 For registered Version 

      send 20 DM or $20 registration fee @{" to " link author}: 
@endnode

